2008年起，费利克斯托南部码头的建设与重新配置开始动工，预备打造{{convert|1.3|km|mi}}的码头及配置13座全新的船对岸型门式起重机。该工程将分两个阶段进行，第一阶段准备於2010年底建成全长750米的海堤，第二阶段则是筹备於2014年开业营运。新码头将有16米的净空，起重机架可适用于超大型的货柜载体。<ref name=CHIL1>{{cite web|url=http://en.hxlogistics.cn/NEWS/Felixstowe-South-reconfiguration-is-started.html |title=Felixstowe South reconfiguration is started |publisher=Century Haixin International Logistics (Shenzhen) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091015165108/http://en.hxlogistics.cn/NEWS/Felixstowe-South-reconfiguration-is-started.html |archivedate=2009-10-15 |accessdate=2015-07-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

===费力克斯托和纳尼顿货运能力计划===
{{Main|伯明翰－彼得伯勒铁路线}}

[[File:CSCL_Globe_arriving_at_Felixstowe,_United_Kingdom.jpg|thumb]]拥有的[[中海环球号|中海环球号]]]]

费利克斯托港与位于[[西海岸主線|西海岸主線]]的纽尼顿之间的[[伯明翰－彼得伯勒线|伯明翰－彼得伯勒线]]铁路轨道已经升级，通过清除W10{{link-en|车辆限界|Loading gauge}}的路线使更多高立方[[货物列车|货物列车]]得以在两地间运转<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.railwaypeople.com/rail-projects/felixstowe-nuneaton-9.html|title=Felixstowe - Nuneaton|work=Railway people|accessdate=2010-05-16}}</ref>。

因为货柜的高立方化，这项计划允许较新的高立方集装箱通过火车运进港口，将会为费利克斯托港的扩张提供更多的货物运输量<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.logisticsmanager.com/Articles/7891/132m+boost+for+rail+freight+.html|title=£132m boost for rail freight|work=Logistics manager|accessdate=2010-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005171947/http://www.logisticsmanager.com/Articles/7891/132m%2Bboost%2Bfor%2Brail%2Bfreight%2B.html|archivedate=2011-10-05}}</ref>。[[英國國營鐵路公司|英國國營鐵路公司]]於2008年完成了[[伊普斯威奇|伊普斯威奇]]至[[彼得伯勒|彼得伯勒]]路线的容量规格提高工作<ref name=PofFdev>{{cite web|url=http://www.portoffelixstowe.co.uk/publications/journal/frmfuturedevelopment.aspx|title=FUTURE DEVELOPMENT|publisher=Port of Felixstowe|accessdate=2010-01-11}}</ref>，全部工作预计2014年完成<ref name=FtN>{{cite web|url=http://www.networkrail.co.uk/browse%20documents/StrategicBusinessPlan/Delivery%20Plan/2009/Enhancements.pdf|title=Enhancements programme: statement of scope, outputs and milestones|publisher=[[英国国营铁路公司|英国国营铁路公司]]|date=2009-03-31|accessdate=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902143019/http://www.networkrail.co.uk/browse%20documents/StrategicBusinessPlan/Delivery%20Plan/2009/Enhancements.pdf|archive-date=2009-09-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，估算耗资2.91亿[[英镑|英镑]]<ref name=netrailFtN>{{cite web|url=http://www.eera.gov.uk/GetAsset.aspx?id=fAAyADUANAAxAHwAfABGAGEAbABzAGUAfAB8ADAAfAA1 |title=Presentation to Regional Transport Forum |publisher=英国国营铁路公司 |date=2009-02-10 |accessdate=2015-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606051050/http://www.eera.gov.uk/GetAsset.aspx?id=fAAyADUANAAxAHwAfABGAGEAbABzAGUAfAB8ADAAfAA1 |archivedate=2011-06-06 }}</ref>。

===科普多可转换站===
{{Main|英格兰A14公路}}

作为费力克斯托南部开发计划的一部分，位处英国{{link-en|英格兰A14公路|A14 road (England)|A14公路}}与A12公路之间的科普多可转换站（Copdock Interchange）将提升容量，而香港[[和记黄埔|和记黄埔]]将为此提供资金支援。<ref name=Inspector>{{cite web|url=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/+/http://www.dft.gov.uk/pgr/shippingports/ports/ir/felixstowesouth/felixstowesouthreconfigurati4953?page=14|title=The effect of the proposed development on safety and the free flow of traffic and its consistency with national transport planning policies|publisher=Department for Transport|accessdate=2010-05-16}}</ref>

